{"tid":2385173,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"GME 69","createTime":"2021-01-29T01:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T03:23:14.000Z","uid":380881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"84bef0008e3c8251571cecd791b18ff7180678ca","tid":2385173,"uid":380881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T01:43:12.000Z","msg":"696969696969"},{"pid":"1ac3bb55f7fbe7f65a71804f3970bdf0a283f029","tid":2385173,"uid":209890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T01:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EbwEJKy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbwEJKy.png&h=121b1791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtrM8be.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdtrM8be.gif&h=9747ad02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ad02b9fa73f2ff02c6d0a51dce287ac8859b4ee","tid":2385173,"uid":70527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T01:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1U68bL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1U68bL.jpg&h=ebb5c24e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3743f4404f5ba6c9868a7996e3d9f2a607f4b719","tid":2385173,"uid":232927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T01:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf90096e23ea9b2359627d9717ac3dfcb4a235b","tid":2385173,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:10:25.000Z","msg":"GME 68<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aJBpbvU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aJBpbvU</a>"},{"pid":"0248fdf3159f17d8bfeabe764c875c5950721d66","tid":2385173,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3743f4404f5ba6c9868a7996e3d9f2a607f4b719","tid":2385173,"uid":232927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T01:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個收錢？"},{"pid":"20a11cb792f4a52e78f004cf0f81ad3d1cbf3f4b","tid":2385173,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:19:14.000Z","msg":"今晚係勝者為王 敗者為寇"},{"pid":"00fead27df18f462b7cd3905e24efdf20edf9b42","tid":2385173,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:22:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">Tesla馬斯克撐散戶　「沽空是個騙局」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n網上討論區Reddit旗下社群「r/WallStreetBets」集合散戶力量齊齊「挾淡倉」，引發遊戲驛站GameStop（美：GME）上演「散戶屠鱷」，惟多間券商聯手出手禁買相關股票。Tesla行政總裁馬斯克（Elon Musk）在Twitter表示，沽空是個騙局，撐散戶味濃。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克此前亦透過Twitter分享了一則呼籲大家一起購買GameStop股票的貼文連結，並簡短打上了一個字「Gamestonk」。此消息曾激發GameStop股價再急升。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2865712/MUSK2_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2865712%2FMUSK2_600.png&h=0a97135a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，Tesla 一直是沽空機構的對象。然而，Tesla股價不斷急升，淡友出動沽空Tesla股票均大幅損手。金析分析公司指出，除了沽空Tesla成為2020年最不賺錢的交易，沽空在家概念或科技股也是最無利可圖的的沽空。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2865712/MUSK1_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2865712%2FMUSK1_600.png&h=7d09c1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你不能賣掉你沒有擁有的房子 <br />\n<br />\n你不能賣掉你沒有擁有的汽車<br />\n<br />\n但你可以賣掉你沒有擁有的股票嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n這是廢話 &ndash;沽空是騙局<br />\n<br />\n合法僅出於歷史的原因"},{"pid":"2b0c9041657091de814fc8b419324b839b99f054","tid":2385173,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">32857</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}